, 'Systemic hormonal contraceptives may be continued, but may not be as effective, during and for up to two weeks following treatment with boceprevir or telaprevir.', 'Major', 'pharmacodynamic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/135933/', '', 'Ulipristal, Estetrol, Diethylstilbestrol, Histrelin, Leuprolide, Bicalutamide, Triptorelin, Goserelin', 'Lamivudine, Paritaprevir, Glecaprevir, Tenofovir alafenamide, Maraviroc, Simeprevir, Cabotegravir, Valaciclovir, Zanamivir, Velpatasvir, Rilpivirine, More', 1767369485);
